{"tid":1947164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冰島發現一人同時感染兩種新冠病毒變體","createTime":"2020-03-28T06:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T07:23:47.000Z","uid":66076,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b9784934c49fbc4dd9d9db2ae9ac11ad1c19ed18","tid":1947164,"uid":66076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:15:04.000Z","msg":"冰島發現一人同時感染兩種新冠病毒變體<br />\n北京新浪網 (2020-03-27 22:01)<br />\n<br />\n據冰島國家廣播公司網站3月24日報導，冰島德科德基因公司的主管卡里&middot;斯特凡松近日在接受新聞採訪時說，到目前為止，該公司已經對冰島新冠肺炎檢測中發現的大約40種新冠病毒變體進行了基因測序，並發現有一人同時感染了兩種新冠病毒變體。<br />\n<br />\n他在採訪中說，這些變體似乎僅在冰島出現。這種病毒極強的變異性也表明，病毒可能從許多不同的國家進入冰島，其來源地區的數量比此前所認為的更多。<br />\n<br />\n而針對一人同時感染兩種新冠病毒變體的情況，卡里介紹說：「我們發現一個人感染了兩種病毒變體：其中一種是帶有特定變異的病毒，另一種是沒有這種變異的病毒。而後來感染的人都只感染了帶有特定變異的病毒。」<br />\n<br />\n這意味著什麼？他說：「這可能只是巧合，但也可能意味著帶有特定變異的病毒比沒有變異的病毒更致命。我們現在不能確定是哪種情況。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，卡里還指出，他們追溯到了每一種病毒變體來自的地區。他說：「有些變體來自奧地利，有一種變體來自在義大利被感染的人，還有一種變體出現在那些在英國被感染的人身上。」<br />\n<br />\n文章編輯 | 王露露<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200327/34681006.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20200327%2F34681006.html&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0Bo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=fa3acbb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200327/34681006.html</a>"},{"pid":"b8f93c2674326650d51b86ee32f474505fae3cf4","tid":1947164,"uid":26354,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:17:04.000Z","msg":"冰島武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"00e6760aa5e492e0cbd3094553395c7ebd138c96","tid":1947164,"uid":35924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"有冇第二個source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705e64e2611d1126f197e97a4f09346fe3b63b2a","tid":1947164,"uid":25582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:19:36.000Z","msg":"王露露"},{"pid":"d151622584a71a9949f2f4357bc5d82fd2abd321","tid":1947164,"uid":106065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:20:58.000Z","msg":"雙重認證"},{"pid":"23525cac73cca889ca4834a13a18daaf90a1f012","tid":1947164,"uid":177485,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"升咗抗寒基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4309817a5dc8e60c94fa8d8c58f8431f250a0d5","tid":1947164,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"大攬炒"},{"pid":"1ec561351abeb8e6e629d5088ba0420ecdb4e25d","tid":1947164,"uid":274161,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"00e6760aa5e492e0cbd3094553395c7ebd138c96","tid":1947164,"uid":35924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"有冇第二個source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:23:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://grapevine.is/news/2020/03/24/patient-infected-with-two-strains-of-covid-19-in-iceland/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgrapevine.is%2Fnews%2F2020%2F03%2F24%2Fpatient-infected-with-two-strains-of-covid-19-in-iceland%2F&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0Bo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=e22cad92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://grapevine.is/news/2020/03/24/patient-infected-with-two-strains-of-covid-19-in-iceland/</a><br />\n<blockquote>K&aacute;ri also noted that <strong>the mutation found in the sample taken from this dually-infected patient is one that has not been found outside Iceland</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, according to international databases.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMore: 冰島科學家發現40種病毒變種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8146565/Scientists-Iceland-claim-FORTY-mutations-coronavirus.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8146565%2FScientists-Iceland-claim-FORTY-mutations-coronavirus.html&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0Bo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=0f64d671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8146565/Scientists-Iceland-claim-FORTY-mutations-coronavirus.html</a><br />\n<blockquote>Scientists in Iceland claim they have found 40 mutations of the coronavirus, which has left the world gripped in fear.<br />\n<br />\nThe mutations were discovered by analysing swabs of COVID-19 patients in Iceland, where almost 600 cases have been reported so far.<br />\n<br />\nThe Icelandic scientists were able to trace the coronavirus back to three European countries &ndash; Austria, Italy &ndash; the epicentre of the outbreak &ndash; and England. <br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"729153d1c6823fc0166b86d6c22c5580ef39ddeb","tid":1947164,"uid":256309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:37:10.000Z","msg":"會唔會上埋格陵蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b56d0c265c36f51e16d3ea48a451bf024ec18c","tid":1947164,"uid":66076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ec561351abeb8e6e629d5088ba0420ecdb4e25d","tid":1947164,"uid":274161,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"00e6760aa5e492e0cbd3094553395c7ebd138c96","tid":1947164,"uid":35924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"有冇第二個source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:23:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://grapevine.is/news/2020/03/24/patient-infected-with-two-strains-of-covid-19-in-iceland/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgrapevine.is%2Fnews%2F2020%2F03%2F24%2Fpatient-infected-with-two-strains-of-covid-19-in-iceland%2F&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0Bo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=e22cad92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://grapevine.is/news/2020/03/24/patient-infected-with-two-strains-of-covid-19-in-iceland/</a><br />\n<blockquote>K&aacute;ri also noted that <strong>the mutation found in the sample taken from this dually-infected patient is one that has not been found outside Iceland</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, according to international databases.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMore: 冰島科學家發現40種病毒變種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8146565/Scientists-Iceland-claim-FORTY-mutations-coronavirus.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8146565%2FScientists-Iceland-claim-FORTY-mutations-coronavirus.html&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0Bo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=0f64d671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8146565/Scientists-Iceland-claim-FORTY-mutations-coronavirus.html</a><br />\n<blockquote>Scientists in Iceland claim they have found 40 mutations of the coronavirus, which has left the world gripped in fear.<br />\n<br />\nThe mutations were discovered by analysing swabs of COVID-19 patients in Iceland, where almost 600 cases have been reported so far.<br />\n<br />\nThe Icelandic scientists were able to trace the coronavirus back to three European countries &ndash; Austria, Italy &ndash; the epicentre of the outbreak &ndash; and England. <br />\n</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:37:20.000Z","msg":"40種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75fd96b1e9072ec14790e92fdc32eccf8a4cdcb","tid":1947164,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516482d8f470506d0b177da9ff1aa9b2151cb7a6","tid":1947164,